{"tid":1583832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際特赦組織昨日向香港警隊放核彈","createTime":"2019-09-20T22:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T00:04:00.000Z","uid":294955,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4d705db62c9f95a7f4b8c3a55c38b2fe9455f7","tid":1583832,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:44:20.000Z","msg":"黑警沒有否認或指控/譴責組織捏造事實，只回應「嚴肅跟進」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TviLOW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TviLOW.jpg&h=719ad5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下文連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190920/mobile/odn-20190920-0920_00176_021.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190920%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190920-0920_00176_021.html&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=d933628a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190920/mobile/odn-20190920-0920_00176_021.html</a><br />\n//國際特赦組織批評警方在反修例示威活動中疑濫捕、暴打被捕人士，甚至在拘押期間施虐，廿一名受訪被捕人士中有十八人需入院，三人留醫逾五天，最長的逾一周，他們聲稱被捕時倒地後仍被虐打，扣查時被人以雷射筆射眼、拒解鎖手機更被威嚇電擊私處。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織本月進行卅八個訪問，當中廿一人在反修例相關示威中被捕，指警方拘捕過程使用不必要及過分武力，當中以防暴警及速龍小隊使用最嚴重暴力。幾乎每名受訪者都聲稱在被捕過程中遭警棍打或拳打。<br />\n<br />\n#雷射筆照眼 威嚇電私處<br />\n有女示威者聲稱被警棍打至倒地，直到雙手被索起。有男示威者稱被捕時遭警棍從後打肩頸，倒地後有警員踢他的臉。入院逾一周的男子稱，被捕時面部及身體多處受傷，遭扣押警署七、八小時才獲送院。此外，一名男子聲稱被扣查時因拒回應提問被打，有警員疑強行睜開及用雷射筆照射其眼。另一男子因拒解鎖手機，稱有警員威嚇要電擊其私處，又聲稱目擊警員逼一名男孩用雷射筆照自己眼睛約廿秒。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他指控，包括有女子聲稱被女警要求脫光搜身；警方以延遲送院為手段逼被捕人錄口供；阻延他們會見律師代表最長達十二小時。組織指警察暴力最常見於拘捕前及拘捕期間，部分疑似示威者頂嘴或不合作而遭受「懲罰」，強烈要求對警察行為作出公正及獨立調查。//<br />\n<br />\n相關連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2019/09/hong-kong-arbitrary-arrests-brutal-beatings-and-torture-in-police-detention-revealed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fnews%2F2019%2F09%2Fhong-kong-arbitrary-arrests-brutal-beatings-and-torture-in-police-detention-revealed%2F&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=22b83bb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2019/09/hong-kong-arbitrary-arrests-brutal-beatings-and-torture-in-police-detention-revealed/</a>"},{"pid":"c836570501c2ab45a8bf2632ba3725d2ccae3b65","tid":1583832,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:44:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"d763a26f7923f230854717926d533903863ea5bc","tid":1583832,"uid":11472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2053126011b8712cdf768f4196ba45a8a1043aa9","tid":1583832,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:51:35.000Z","msg":"希望真係會有制裁同懲罰"},{"pid":"8c97aa6da63232411a2a02da44c257a140680b27","tid":1583832,"uid":6086,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2053126011b8712cdf768f4196ba45a8a1043aa9","tid":1583832,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:51:35.000Z","msg":"希望真係會有制裁同懲罰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:54:54.000Z","msg":"就算坐監都有警務人員專用監倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工打人又係納稅人養<br />\n打完人坐監又係納稅人養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2f1a48e644914e4a005f953cd4455878c0089c","tid":1583832,"uid":268038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea4d705db62c9f95a7f4b8c3a55c38b2fe9455f7","tid":1583832,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T22:44:20.000Z","msg":"黑警沒有否認或指控/譴責組織捏造事實，只回應「嚴肅跟進」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TviLOW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TviLOW.jpg&h=719ad5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />